          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Photon flux integrated from the threshold to the",
                " end-point energy was obtained from the activities of",
                " the (g,n) reaction products of seven elements with",
                " threshold energy from 8.02 to 12.22 MeV (Au, As, Ir,",
                "  Mn, Ni, Se, Sn).",
                "These foils were irradiated with Er to determine the",
                " absolute flux assuming linear shape of the photon",
                " flux up to ~12 MeV.",
                "It results to the 1.24+/-0.21E+08 photons/cm2/sec for",
                " the energy range from 9.2 MeV (162Er(g,n) threshold)",
                " to 14 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
